{"tid":573312,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一句]留低一句你仲記得老師講過嘅古文","createTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:48.000Z","uid":40170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf8cbe4360437b4aabe0885d62b3d54472b330b","tid":573312,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"今游俠，其行雖不軌於正義，然其言必信，其行必果，已諾必誠，不愛其軀，赴士之厄困，既已存亡死生矣，而不矜其能，羞伐其德，蓋亦有足多者焉。<br />\n<br />\n- 《史記 &middot; 游俠列傳》<br />\n<br />\n老師真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時心情唔好 放break會主動問候吓 真係赴士之厄困<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩要搵推薦人永無say no<br />\n永遠睇到學生好嘅一面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗其行雖不軌於正義之外<br />\n真係好似游俠咁幫學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}